Message: Hi babe, did you get home ok last night?
Yes. Thanks for waiting for me until my mum showed up.
Its fine :) What are you up to this weekend?
I have to look after my little brother as my mum is at work. How about you?
Not much really, will probably see some mates later. Hey maybe we could meet up sometime?
That would be fab.
Ok, I'll message you soon. It was great to meet you last night :)
Morning sleepy babe. How are you today?
I'm good, how are you?
I'm good. I've been thinking about you. Do you want to meet up on Wednesday?
Love to :) What time?
What time do you finish school?
Meet you in the rec at 4pm then?
Gr8.
See you then. I can't wait.
Hi Lottie, need some company tonight? ;)
Are you offering?!
Can I come round?
I would like you to, but I don't think mum would be happy as I'm babysitting. How are you?
Pretty good thanks, how about you?
I'm good, just a bit bored.
I'm really looking forward to seeing you on Weds.
Me too :)
Are you going to be wearing what you wore at the disco?!
LOL no, I'll be in my school uniform unfortunately. :/
Even better! ;)
My mums back, I've got to go. See you on Weds :)
Bye babes, can't wait to see you.
I had such a good time this afternoon. I wish we could have spent longer together.
Me too. Sorry I had to leave, but mum doesn't like me staying out late.
I totally understand, I just wish I could be with you ALL the time.
That's sweet.
Well I think you're really sweet. When can we meet up again?
I'm not sure. Maybe the weekend?
How about Saturday? I really wanted to kiss you today, but I wasn't sure if you wanted me to.
blushing
So how about Saturday then? Can we make it a date for a kiss?
Yes. I'd like that.
Great :) xxx
Hi Lottie, how are you? I can't stop thinking about (all) of you. I think you are amazing.
I'm really good. I keep thinking about you too.
What sort of things are you thinking? I keep thinking about how pretty you are.
I'm blushing! Do you really think that?
Of course. You are beautiful. I love your hair. Gorg!
No one has ever said that to me before. Apart from my mum! lol
Well it's the truth.
Thanks. I think you are great too.
That makes me really happy to know that.
I'm really looking forward to seeing you tomorrow.
Me too!
What shall we do?
I don't mind really, you choose :)
How about we grab a bite somewhere together?
Sounds perfect.
Had such a great time yesterday. I wish I could see more of you.
I did too. How about we meet up next week?
That wasn't quite what I meant ;)
What did you mean then?
I meant that I wish I could see more of your body, if you know what I mean... ;)
Oh I see! blushes
So what do you say? Will you take some special pictures of yourself for me?
Hmm I'm not sure. I'd feel embarrassed. What if someone else saw them?
There's nothing to be embarrassed about. You are beautiful. I just really want to see what's under your clothes.
Um, I'm not sure I'm ready...
Ok, that's ok, but I just wanted to tell you what I wanted... Shall we meet up next week then? Are you free after school on Tuesday?
Yes, I am. Where shall we meet?
How about the coffee shop round the corner from your school?
Yep ok, see you there about 4?
Perfect. Can't wait. Xxx
It was great seeing you today. I can't stop thinking about how cute you are. I really WANT you babes.
Aw that is really sweet! I had lots of fun today.
When can we get together again?
The weekend?
But that's ages away! :(
I know! Sorry, it's just that I'm really busy with school and stuff.
Ok I understand. But I'll miss you like crazy.
I'll miss you too.
I'm not sure I can wait that long... Can I ask you to do something for me?
Yes of course, what is it?
I really want to see you without your clothes on.
But I said I wasn't sure if I wanted to do that...
I know you did but I just want you so much.
But I don't think it's a good idea. I'm sorry.
That's ok, I'm sorry for asking. I just think you're amazing and I want to be close to you.
It's ok, I understand. I want to be close to you too.
